            text: '<p>\n\t<strong>动词短语</strong></p>\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%;" width="680">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t有些动词由两至三个词组成。有的 multiword verbs 可用句子宾语分隔，有的不能。<br />\n\t\t\t\t请看下列不可分隔多词动词的例子。注意，在句中使用时，动词中的所有词必须放在一起。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>https://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/17/88/v/111788/GE_5.6.2.2.2_1_v2.mp3</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>Let&#39;s <strong>look for</strong> some classic jeans.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我们找几条经典牛仔裤。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>https://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/17/89/v/111789/GE_5.6.2.2.2_2_v2.mp3</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>I can&#39;t <strong>keep up with</strong> the trends.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我跟不上潮流。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t下列多词动词可以分隔。注意，动词中的单词既能在一起，也可用句子宾语分隔。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/17/90/v/111790/GE_5.6.2.2.2_3_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>I <strong>put on</strong> my tie. </em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我戴上领带。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/17/91/v/111791/GE_5.6.2.2.2_4_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>I <strong>put </strong>my tie <strong>on</strong>.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我戴上领带。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/17/92/v/111792/GE_5.6.2.2.2_5_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>I <strong>tried on</strong> 14 baseball caps. </em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我试戴了 14 顶棒球帽。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 5%;">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/17/87/v/111787/GE_5.6.2.2.2_6_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 30%;">\n\t\t\t\t<em>I <strong>tried</strong> 14 baseball caps <strong>on</strong>.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我试戴了 14 顶棒球帽。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<br />',
